Interface IChainable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAsyncAIComponent, AbstractSimpleAIComponent, AgentActionAIComponent, AgentAI, AgentAngleAIComponent, AgentLocationAIComponent, AgentVelocityAIComponent, BallLocationAIComponent, BoundryCheckAIComponent, GameState, GoalLocationAIComponent, HomeAreaAIComponent, MovementAreaAIComponent, PlayersLocationAIComponent, PlayModeAIComponent

    public interface IChainable
    This interface represents a contract for objects that can be connected in a chain. Each chainable object should be able to be connected to another via the setNext method. Each object should also be able to accept an object of type EnvironmentModel via the setNext() method. Created by raghavnarula on 03/11/2015.
